  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK709">
<l>pakaimaiyuṅ kēṇmaiyuṅ kaṇṇuraikkum kaṇṇiṉ </l>
<l>vakaimai yuṇarvārp peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a king gets ministers who can read the movements of the eye, the eyes (of foreign kings) will (themselves) reveal (to him) their hatred or friendship.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
